    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Cup of the Alicorn (Fetish)</strong></p><p><em>Creation Cost: 6 Gnosis.</em></p><p><strong>Effect:</strong></p><ul><li>Any poison or disease poured into the cup is neutralized.</li><li>As a bonus action, you may drink from the cup to gain advantage on your next saving throw against poison or disease.</li></ul><p>The effect lasts until you complete a long rest (ST discretion).</p><p><strong>Fetish Rating:</strong> 2. <strong>Minimum Max Gnosis:</strong> 5. Cannot use while raging unless this fetish states otherwise. Spirit Attention: you can have a number of actively empowered fetishes equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum 1); instantaneous effects do not count after resolution.</p><p><code>[GAROU_FETISH] id=cup-of-the-alicorn; rating=2; minGnosis=5; activation=action</code></p>",
      "chat": "<p>Fetish (Rating 2). Min Max Gnosis 5. Activate: action — Force (Wisdom/Gnosis check DC 12) or Appease (spend 1 Gnosis). Cup neutralizes poison/disease poured in; bonus action drink for advantage on next save vs poison or disease.</p>"
    },
